data.description: Immaculate 2-story townhome situated on a landscaped green space. Brand new carpet throughout the entire living space and new luxury flooring in the kitchen. Spacious kitchen includes all appliances (brand new microwave), and the washer & dryer too. Nothing to do except move in! Separate eating area, family room features a cozy fireplace and tons of natural light. 2 bedrooms located upstairs, along with the full bath and large soaking tub. The basement offers storage galore and the option to add a 3rd bedroom or additional living space. Garage is attached and oversized, visitor parking is right across the way. Olde Town Arvada, light rail, Apex, Ralston Creek Trail, restaurants & shops are all close by. These rarely come on the market and this one checks all the boxes. Ask about a credit to buy down the rate which can significantly lower your monthly mortgage payments and make homeownership even more affordable!
